name: Senna SeaFluffle
description: Meet Senna! Senna is an average sized fluffle coat, color, ears, tail are all common. However Senna does posses a rare double frill!    A very easy going Fluffle with a playful personality, Senna enjoys the outdoors and rainy weather. They can be a little protective of their blankets and nap time. Exercise caution when walking them for walkies.
